    • Method Detail

      • isInService

        boolean isInService()
        Return whether this FIX source is currently in service.
        Returns:
        True if this FIX source is currently in service, false otherwise. Note that this is a best effort result only. A true does not imply that a subsequent call to IFIXSource.fireMessage(com.camerontec.catalys.core.message.IFIXMessage) will succeed and a false valued does not imply that a subsequent call to IFIXSource.fireMessage(com.camerontec.catalys.core.message.IFIXMessage) will fail.
